--------------+----------------------------------+\n|                id                |  name |             user_id              |            tenant_id             |\n+----------------------------------+-------+----------------------------------+----------------------------------+\n| 1c39fab0fa9a4a68b307e7ce1535c62b | admin | 3b71182dc36e45c6be4733d508201694 | 5b0af1d5013746b286b0d650da73be57 |\n+----------------------------------+-------+----------------------------------+----------------------------------+\n\n3) Remove a role from that user that they don't have (using otherrole here since devstack sets it up):\n\n$ keystone --os-user=blktest1 --os-pass=blkpwd --os-tenant-name service user-role-remove --user blktest1 --role anotherrole --tenant service\n\n- Expected to fail with 404, but it doesn't!\n\n4) List roles as that user:\n\n$ keystone --os-user=blktest1 --os-pass=blkpwd --os-tenant-name service user-role-list\n+----------------------------------+-------------+----------------------------------+----------------------------------+\n|                id                |     name    |             user_id              |            tenant_id             |\n+----------------------------------+-------------+----------------------------------+----------------------------------+\n| 1c39fab0fa9a4a68b307e7ce1535c62b |    admin    | 3b71182dc36e45c6be4733d508201694 | 5b0af1d5013746b286b0d650da73be57 |\n| afe23e7955704ccfad803b4a104b28a7 | anotherrole | 3b71182dc36e45c6be4733d508201694 | 5b0af1d5013746b286b0d650da73be57 |\n+----------------------------------+-------------+----------------------------------+----------------------------------+\n\n- Expected to not include the role that was just removed!\n\n5) Remove the role again:\n\n$ keystone --os-user=blktest1 --os-pass=blkpwd --os-tenant-name service user-role-remove --user blktest1 --role anotherrole --tenant service\n\n- No errors, which I guess is expected since list just said they had the role...\n\n6) List roles, and now it's gone:\n\n$ keystone --os-user=blktest1 --os-pass=blkpwd --os-tenant-name service user-role-list\n+----------------------------------+-------+----------------------------------+----------------------------------+\n|                id                |  name |             user_id              |            tenant_id             |\n+----------------------------------+-------+----------------------------------+----------------------------------+\n| 1c39fab0fa9a4a68b307e7ce1535c62b | admin | 3b71182dc36e45c6be4733d508201694 | 5b0af1d5013746b286b0d650da73be57 |\n+----------------------------------+-------+----------------------------------+----------------------------------+\n\n7) Remove role again:\n\n$ keystone --os-user=blktest1 --os-pass=blkpwd --os-tenant-name service user-role-remove --user blktest1 --role anotherrole --tenant service\nCould not find user, 3b71182dc36e45c6be4733d508201694. (HTTP 404)\n\n- Strangely says user not found rather than role not assigned.", "owner_link": "https://bugs.launchpad.net/api/devel/~blk-u", "bug_tasks_collection_link": "https://bugs.launchpad.net/api/devel/bugs/1242855/bug_tasks", "duplicate_of_link": null, "date_created": "2013-10-21T19:17:53.287750+00:00", "activity_collection_link": "https://bugs.launchpad.net/api/devel/bugs/1242855/activity", "subscriptions_collection_link": "https://bugs.launchpad.net/api/devel/bugs/1242855/subscriptions", "date_last_updated": "2014-04-17T07:56:36.935447+00:00", "who_made_private_link": null, "date_made_private": null, "heat": 256, "bug_watches_collection_link": "https://bugs.launchpad.net/api/devel/bugs/1242855/bug_watches", "cves_collection_link": "https://bugs.launchpad.net/api/devel/bugs/1242855/cves", "duplicates_collection_link": "https://bugs.launchpad.net/api/devel/bugs/1242855/duplicates", "attachments_collection_link": "https://bugs.launchpad.net/api/devel/bugs/1242855/attachments", "security_related": true, "latest_patch_uploaded": null, "tags": [], "date_last_message